    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>Generated from:  MR::FreeFormBestFit

Class to accumulate source and target points for free form alignment
Calculates best Free Form transform to fit given source-&gt;target deformation
origin ref grid as box corners ( resolution parameter specifies how to divide box )
</verbatim> </para>
